              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-bellmead" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Bellmead Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Bellmead (I-35) charges court costs plus a $10 fee — submit a notarized plea form and Type 3A record by your appearance date; 90 days.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-beverly-hills" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Beverly Hills Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Beverly Hills Municipal Court (McLennan County, TX — a small city within Waco, not California) hasn't posted its standard DSC fee online — call (254) 752-2584 ext. 2 by your appearance date to confirm. Complete your</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-bruceville-eddy" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Bruceville Eddy Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Got a ticket in Bruceville-Eddy (McLennan County, I-35 south of Waco)? The municipal court charges $144 to dismiss a traffic ticket via Driver Safety Course. Take a</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-crawford" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Crawford Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Crawford Municipal Court (McLennan County, west of Waco) charges a $144 court admin fee ($169 in a school zone) to dismiss a ticket via Driver Safety Course — submit your notarized form before your appearance date.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-golinda" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Golinda Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Got a speeding ticket in Golinda (McLennan County, south of Waco)? The Golinda Municipal Court hasn't posted its DSC fee online — call (254) 881-7333 before your appearance date to request dismissal via Driver Safety Course. Take the</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-hewitt" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Hewitt Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Hewitt (I-35) charges $144 ($169 school zone) by money order — request in person or by mail by your appearance date; 90 days to finish.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-lacy-lakeview" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Lacy Lakeview Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Lacy Lakeview (I-35) takes a written DSC request by your appearance date — call (254) 799-2458 for the court costs; disposition within 20 business days.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-lorena" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Lorena Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Lorena Municipal Court (McLennan County, I-35 S of Waco) charges a $144 court fee ($169 school zone) to dismiss a ticket via driver safety course — mail your notarized application by your court date.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-mart" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Mart Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Mart (US-84) takes a written DSC request by your appearance date — call (254) 876-2462 to confirm the court costs; 90 days, Type 3A record.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-mcgregor" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Mcgregor Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">McGregor Municipal Court (McLennan County, US-84 SW of Waco) charges $143.90 to dismiss a traffic ticket via Driver Safety Course — request by your appearance date. Take your course online for</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-moody" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Moody Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Moody Municipal Court (McLennan County, SW of Waco) charges $143.90 to dismiss a ticket via Driver Safety Course — submit your notarized reply form by your appearance date. Complete a state-approved course for</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-riesel" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Riesel Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Riesel Municipal Court (McLennan County, SE of Waco) charges a $144 court fee to take a driver safety course and dismiss a qualifying ticket — call (254) 896-6501 ext. 1 within 10 days of your citation. Complete a state-approved course for</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-robinson" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Robinson Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Robinson charges $144 ($169 school zone) — get court approval before taking the course; submit a Type 3A record within 90 days.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-west" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">West Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">West (I-35) charges a $144 fee — submit the Request Form in person or by mail; 90 days and a certified DPS record required.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border align-top">
                <td class="py-3 pr-4"><a href="/texas/courts/mclennan-municipal-woodway" class="text-primary-deep font-semibold hover:underline">Woodway Municipal Court</a></td>
                <td class="py-3 text-text-body">Woodway (SH-6) charges $144 ($169 school zone) and takes DSC requests online or in person by your appearance date; 90 days to finish.</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-text-body text-base leading-7 mb-10 mt-4" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">
          <p>Don't see your court? Search every Texas court in our <a href="/texas/courts" class="text-primary-deep font-medium hover:underline">court directory</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">Frequently asked questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-8 mb-12">
          {faqs.map(item => (
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">{item.q}</h3>
              <p class="text-text-body text-base leading-7" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;" set:html={item.a} />
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">Take the Waco course that every court accepts</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-text-body text-base leading-7 mb-8" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">
          <p>Once your court approves the request, our TDLR-approved course is accepted at every Waco-area court — $28, fully online, with the certificate the moment you finish.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-10">
          <a href={enrollUrl} class="inline-flex bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-white h-[56px] px-8 rounded-[16px] text-lg font-semibold items-center justify-center no-underline" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; box-shadow: 0px 10px 15px -3px rgba(17,23,34,0.08), 0px 4px 6px -4px rgba(17,23,34,0.05);">
            Start the $28 Course →
